			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The developers have used 75 as a break point on stats.  
<br />

<br />
I have personally tested the difference between 70 and 75 agility.  It was very noticable.  {Either that or the Random number generater was on one if its strange streaks.}  
<br />

<br />
I do not have personal experince with dex, put I suspect it also a break point at 75 and it has noticable difference as well.  
<br />

<br />
For the High Elf, I would consider putting the 5 points into dex instead of Stammina.
<br />

<br />
For the Erudite, I would condsider putting 5 points in Agi instead of stammina and 5 points from Int into Dex.  {However, if you are playing a Erudite, you are going for max Int at the expense of other stats, so maybe not}
<br />

<br />
I make these recommendations from my experince.  Currently, my highest character is 54th and I have not seen the AE attack mobs or the High Level encounters.  When I start experincing these encounters, I might change my mind, but with what I know now, I would defineatly have a min of 75 Agi and would heavily consider getting a min of 75 in Dex.<br />_________________<br />Dabrighter Blazemeister
