			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">At levels 16, 29, and 44 night vision is not a concern.
<br />

<br />
Level 16 magicians can summon Heatstones which grant worn Infravision, the same as Gnomes and High Elves.
<br />

<br />
Level 29 magicians summon Coldstones, which grants Dark Elf Ultravision.
<br />

<br />
Level 44 magicians can now summon Orbs of Exploration after adventuring in Miragul's Menagerie, which grants Plainsight (combination See Invisible and Ultravision), which is vastly superior to even Ultravision.
<br />

<br />
So after level 16, most races are equal in vision, and after level 29, all races are equal in terms of vision.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
		</table></td>
	</tr>
